      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "OP: &quot;How can I use the @link tag to link to a method?&quot; The <i>@link</i> tag can be used inline within a paragraph, as requested by the OP. The <i>@see</i> tag cannot. See more detail at <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/10097199/javadoc-see-or-link\">this question</a>."
